; RFC-0086 PR-2H — Tool_args + Tool_result shared types extraction.
; Identified as the real cycle blocker behind PR-2E iter2's
; "Tool_misc_web_fetch" classification (plan §8.16 / §8.20 audit
; 2026-05-15): the 5-module tool_* cluster has *zero* cycles with
; keeper_* / Prometheus / Activity_graph; the only blocker is that
; Tool_args (335+199 LoC) and Tool_result (250+85 LoC) reside in
; parent masc_mcp, so keeper namespace promotion would create a
; sub-lib -> parent direction.
;
; Extracting these two as a leaf sub-lib unblocks both keeper
; namespace bulk promotion (PR-2E) and the Tool_misc_web_fetch
; cluster RFC.
;
; Deps: yojson only (Tool_args.mli's Tool_local_runtime_core reference
; is a single OCamldoc cross-reference comment, not a code dep).
; (wrapped false) keeps bare `Tool_args` / `Tool_result` so all
; 1156 external refs (Tool_args 161 bare + 4 wrapped, Tool_result
; 969 bare + 22 wrapped) need only the 26 wrapped refs sed'd to bare.
(include_subdirs no)

(library
 (name masc_mcp_tool_types)
 (public_name masc_mcp.tool_types)
 (wrapped false)
 (libraries yojson masc_log masc_core eio time_compat)
 (preprocess (pps ppx_deriving_yojson)))
